name: Series 100 Silicone Facepiece
meta_description: Facepiece assembly, Small, Silicone Rubber
short_description:
• Low-profile design

  • Multi-position cartridge placement

  • Extra large inhalation valves

  • Patented corrugated exhale valve

  • Low "dead air" space

  • Unique low-fitting design

  • Textured non-slip face seal

  • Swivel strap retainers

  • Replaceable parts
summary:
U.S. Safety sets the standard for comfort and compatibility with Comfort-Air™ series respirators. Molded from pure silicone, the wide interior flange, deep chin cup and rolled edges of the Comfort-Air™ mask make it the “hands down” favorite for long-term comfort and fit.
The textured no-slip face seal and swivel retainers ensure proper placement. Extra large inhalation valve, unique corrugated exhale valve and minimized “dead air” space provide low breathing resistance and added comfort.
Patented multi-position cartridge placement and low-fitting mask design allow maximum compatibility with other PPE. NIOSH approved.
size_info: Facepiece assembly, Medium, Silicone Rubber

summary:
U.S. Safety's NEW Flat-Fold N95 Disposable Respirator delivers maximum breathing comfort and fit in a convenient package.
Easy donning with a single, continuous strap and no staples. The large cavity provides easier, cooler breathing and allows for un-inhibited speech. An optional valved version provides enhanced breathing comfort.

name: Diskit P100 Particulate Filters
meta_description: Lightweight and ultra-low profile, the Diskit™ revolutionizes comfort and compatibility.
description: Lightweight and ultra-low profile, the Diskit™ revolutionizes comfort and compatibility.
short_description:
• Lightweight - only 0.8 oz.

  • Ultra-low profile

  • Crush-proof internal frame

  • Low breathing resistance

  • Multi-position connector

  • Extended filter life*

  • Available welding spark shield

  • Rigid Internal Frame

  • Offset Filter Connection

  • Diskit Cartridge Construction
summary:
Light weight and ultra low-profile, the Diskit™ P100 Filter from U.S. Safety revolutionizes wearer comfort and compatibility with other PPE.
The offset connector allows the filter to be positioned three different ways on the mask to maximize wearer visibility as well as compatibility with other PPE, such as safety glasses, goggles, face shields and welding helmets.
Only 5/8 “ thick, the Diskit™ weighs just 0.8 oz, yet the rigid internal frame prevents crushing and extends filter life. Patented space plenums allow the filter media to evenly “load” to the edge, resulting in noticeably lower breathing resistance compared to standard filters.
Diskit™ is compatible with U.S. Safety Comfort-Air™ and Comfort-Ease™ Respirators.
Welding Application: Patented spark shield protects the filter from sparks and welding splatter.
size_info: P100 particulate filter, minimum 99.97% efficient protection against oil & non-oil particulates (10 pr/box, case qty: 10)

name: Series 97LP Respirator Assemblies
short_description:
Both Series 97LP and 152 feature a uniquely designed facepiece that provides maximum seal with a wide sealing edge that fits securely against the face. Large exhalation valves reduce breathing resistance and assure greater worker acceptance.
Both are approved for use with hose lengths up to 300ft.
The Series 97LP Low Pressure Half-Mask Respirator is specifically designed for use with a low-pressure air supply source.
size_info: Complete Supplied Air Half-Mask Respirator for low pressure, less main air supply hose

name: Series 152 Respirator Assemblies
short_description:
Both Series 97LP and 152 feature a uniquely designed facepiece that provides maximum seal with a wide sealing edge that fits securely against the face. Large exhalation valves reduce breathing resistance and assure greater worker acceptance.
Both are approved for use with hose lengths up to 300ft.
The Series 152's airflow control valve regulates airflow for comfort adjustment by the wearer. For use with air compressors.
size_info: Complete Air Supplied Half-Mask Respirator, less main air supply hose

name: Sand Viper with Clear Lens
meta_description:
Uncompromised protection from wind, dust and airborne debris. Breathable, fog-free comfort with a secure fit for confidence even in the harshest environments.
Rugged, versatile protection from wind, dust and debris for harsh environments.
description:
Uncompromised protection from wind, dust and airborne debris. Breathable, fog-free comfort with a secure fit for confidence even in the harshest environments.
Rugged, versatile protection from wind, dust and debris for harsh environments.
short_description:
• Vented EVA Foam

  • Advanced Fog-Free System

  • Optional Strap

  • Available Bifocal

  • Blocks Harmful UV

  • High Impact Protection
summary:
Airborne particles are the leading cause of eye injuries in the workplace. The Sand Viper™'s superior fit and performance make it the choice of professionals for harsh conditions where airborne dust and debris are present.
Sand Viper™'s optional strap and vented foam backing create a secure, goggle-like fit with the comfort and breathability of safety glasses. The high-performance fog-free, scratch-resistant coating puts Sand Viper™ ahead of all others in performance and durability.
Sand Viper™ is now available with +1.50, +2.00 and +2.50 magnifiers for reading and close-up work (clear lens only).
size_info: Black frame w/foam spatula temple & strap, clear anti-fog lens

name: InfraSpec Shade 2.0
meta_description:
Convenient, Flip-up Infrared and impact protection in a lightweight, Rx'able design.
InfraSpec™ is IR Protection On Demand.
description:
Convenient, Flip-up Infrared and impact protection in a lightweight, Rx'able design.
InfraSpec™ is IR Protection On Demand.
short_description:
• Flip-Up IR Shade Lens

  • Adjustable Nosepiece

  • High Impact Protection

  • Rx Capable

  • Blocks Harmful IR* and UV
summary:
nfraSpec™ offers the ultimate versatility for protection against IR hazards. The flip-down IR filter lens can be deployed instantly when you need it, without the need to change eyewear. Clear lenses provide high-impact protection at all times.
Prescription lenses can be installed for the ultimate in convenience for Rx wearers. InfraSpec™ reduces the risk of eye injury from impact by combining optional IR protection and impact protection in a single design with all-day comfort.
*Infrared (IR) protection only provide when shaded IR filter lens is in the down position.
Exposure to high levels of infrared radiation without proper eye protection has been linked to the development of various forms of permanent damage to the eye, including cataracts. Consult OSHA Standards to select the appropriate IR shade according to the hazard/application.
size_info: Green IR Shade 2.0

name: P100 Diskit  Replacement Filter 10/box
description:
Light weight and ultra low-profile, the Diskit® P100 Filter from Dentec Safety revolutionizes wearer comfort and compatibility with other PPE.
The offset connector allows the filter to be positioned three different ways on the mask to maximize wearer visibility as well as compatibility with other PPE, such as safety glasses, goggles, face shields and welding helmets.
Only 5/8" thick, the Diskit® weighs just 0.8 oz, yet the rigid internal frame prevents crushing and extends filter life. Patented space plenums allow the filter media to evenly "load" to the edge, resulting in noticeably lower breathing resistance ompared to standard filters.
Diskit® is compatible with Dentec Safety Comfort-Air® and Comfort-Ease™ Respirators.
summary:
• P100 particulate filter
  • minimum 99.97% efficient protection against oil & non-oil particulates
  • (10 pr/box).
